title: Douglas Valentine: The Phoenix Program (2011)
description:
VISIT: https://archive.politicalassassinations.net/
This is a talk from the 2011 Coalition on Political Assassinations Conference. Douglas Valentine, author of 'The Phoenix Program' discusses the his book and the CIA's Vietnam War assassination program by the same name. Original video of the talk came from on COPA's ustream channel (no longer available).

For more related content, please visit: 
http://ourhiddenhistory.org/
https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
